                    </div>
                    <div class="aTopRight">
                        <p>Complain Connect specializes in managing <br> complaint portals for societies. Our business <br> revolves around providing a platform where <br> residents can submit complaints related to <br> various issues within their society, such as <br> maintenance, security, or facilities. </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="aboutBtm">

                    <div class="aBtmLeft">
                        <p>Complain Connect streamlines the complaint <br> process by offering a user-friendly interface for <br> residents to lodge their concerns efficiently.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="aBtmRight">

                        <h1 id="firsth1">What</h1>
